channel.title: Comments on: First Order of Business

item.title: By: Kent
item.dc:creator: Kent
item.description: On top of owning an RX-7 once more, I give you kudos for passing legally. :D If I wasn't so trashed this past weekend, I would've visited you. lol
item.content:encoded: On top of owning an RX-7 once more, I give you kudos for passing legally. :D If I wasn’t so trashed this past weekend, I would’ve visited you. lol

item.title: By: Eric
item.dc:creator: Eric
item.description: Yeah, not my tastes either... The spoiler is a Racing Beat, basically an upsized '99 wing. The sideskirts I'm not sure, maybe Pettit or something, but they're the worst part.
item.content:encoded: Yeah, not my tastes either… The spoiler is a Racing Beat, basically an upsized ’99 wing. The sideskirts I’m not sure, maybe Pettit or something, but they’re the worst part.

item.title: By: Jackson Tran

item.description: If you're going back to stock, we're gonna be matching! And I agree, those 99 spec parts don't look too nice
